description: Jouslain Tytania is one of the four dukes in line to succeed Ajman Tytania as the clan`s next Landless Lord. He is seen by some as the favored out of the four dukes to succeed Ajman. Jouslain prefers to resolve disputes using diplomacy over military force or scheming. Jouslain flagship is called the Austra.
name: Jouslain Tytania
